  <summary date="2019-08-19T20:34:34Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Venezuela Humanitarian Relief, Reconstruction, and Rule of Law Act of 2018

This bill provides for humanitarian aid for the people of Venezuela, in light of the humanitarian and political crisis there. It also provides for (1) sanctions against those responsible for corruption and narcotics trafficking in Venezuela, (2)&#160;efforts to help rebuild the country's infrastructure and restructure its&#160;debt, and (3) efforts to otherwise address the humanitarian and political crisis.</summary>
